    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNeovim crashes when opening [`:Neogit`](https://github.com/NeogitOrg/neogit) with [`statuscol.nvim`](https://github.com/luukvbaal/statuscol.nvim) installed, Neogit works fine without it. Some interactions between two plugins probably caused the crash.\r\n\r\nASAN log: [nvim_asan.txt](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/files/12136774/nvim_asan.txt)\r\n\r\nThere's no [backtrace](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/wiki/FAQ#backtrace-linux) when compiling with asan enabled. I will compile neovim without asan if it's necessary.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nRun `nvim -c 'Neogit'` -> crash\r\n\r\nI will try to reproduce with minimal config when I have some time.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nnot crash\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.10.0-dev-703+gd2efcbf2d\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\n-\n\n### Operating system/version\n\narch\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nalacritty 0.12.2\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from repo",
